# Copy this file to ".env" and fill in your key.

# Required: your Anthropic API key.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# Optional: override the model (defaults to claude-sonnet-4-6).
# ANTHROPIC_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-6

# Optional: restrict all file operations to this directory (defaults to the
# current working directory). Keep it pointed at the project root for the demo.
# FS_TOOLS_BASE_DIR=.
